 the next day; but as soon as the wife was awake she went to the house, and the next morning when the son of the woman was asleep she had the following words: "The son of the poor man will do us no harm, and will be delivered from a dreadful curse."   
 

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                
